Installation:

    1) install vim
    2) delete _vimrc
    3) cd into vimfiles
    3) clone online repo using
    git clone https://github.com/tvandersar/VimWithSubmodules_2015.git    

Create symlinks in cmd:
    
    cd "c:Program Files (x86)\Vim"
    mklink /H "c:Program Files (x86)\Vim\_vimrc" "c:Program Files (x86)\Vim\vimfiles\_vimrc"

Switch to the vimfiles directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd vimfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update

